OL,3,CInterim Chief Constable appointed at
OL,4,CGloucestershire Police
OL,6,FGloucestershire Police has appointed a
OL,7,Fnew interim Chief Constable, following
OL,8,Fthe suspension of its former leader.
OL,10,FMaggie Blyth is being seconded from
OL,11,Fthe College of Policing and will take
OL,12,Fup the role on Tuesday 22 October.
OL,14,FIt's only the second time in the
OL,15,Fforce's 185-year history that a woman
OL,16,Fhas been at the helm.
