OL,3,CInterim Chief Constable appointed at
OL,4,CGloucestershire Police
OL,6,FHer appointment follows the suspension
OL,7,Fof Rod Hansen on 8 October, who is
OL,8,Fcurrently under investigation by the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC) following allegations of gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct.
OL,13,FChris Nelson, Gloucestershire's Police
OL,14,Fand Crime Commissioner (PCC), said:
OL,15,F"Over the last week, I have been
OL,16,Fcompletely focused on making an
OL,17,Finterim appointment to bring in an
OL,18,Fexperienced leader to fulfil the
OL,19,Fresponsibilities of a Chief Constable.
