OL,6,F"Bringing in someone as nationally
OL,7,Frespected as Maggie Blyth is very good
OL,8,Fnews for the county," he said.
OL,10,FGloucestershire Police will have been
OL,11,Fwithout a chief or a deputy for a
OL,12,Ffortnight by the time she begins the
OL,13,Frole.
OL,15,FEarlier this month, it was revealed
OL,16,FGloucestershire Police's Deputy Chief
OL,17,FConstable Shaun West retired in June
OL,18,Famidst a criminal investigation over
OL,19,Falleged assaults and misconduct in a
OL,20,Fpublic office.
