OL,6,FThe IOPC has confirmed to ITV News
OL,7,Fthat the cases of Hansen and West are
OL,8,Fseparate.
OL,10,FCommenting on her new interim role, Ms
OL,11,FBlyth said: "It is an honour to be
OL,12,Fleading Gloucestershire Constabulary,
OL,13,Fthe oldest county force in the
OL,14,Fcountry, with officers and staff who
OL,15,Fexemplify what it means to be a public
OL,16,Fservant.
