OL,6,F"My intention is to lead the Force
OL,7,Fduring this chapter and provide
OL,8,Fofficers and staff with stability and
OL,9,Fleadership to meet the vision of the
OL,10,FPolice and Crime Prevention Plan set
OL,11,Fbetween the Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioner and the public."
OL,14,FMs Blyth has more than 30 years' of
OL,15,Fexperience as a public servant,
OL,16,Fstarting her career in the probation
OL,17,Fservice before going on to specialise
OL,18,Fin youth justice.
