OL,6,FShe has also worked for local
OL,7,Fgovernment child protection services,
OL,8,Fwhere she had senior oversight of
OL,9,Fchild protection arrangements, and
OL,10,Fworked on several high-profile child
OL,11,Fsexual exploitation and domestic
OL,12,Fhomicide operations.
OL,14,FShe was promoted to assistant chief
OL,15,Fconstable in May 2019, overseeing
OL,16,Flocal policing and public protection
OL,17,Facross Hampshire.
