OL,3,CInterim Chief Constable appointed at
OL,4,CGloucestershire Police
OL,6,FIn October 2021, she took up the role
OL,7,Fof National Police Lead for violence
OL,8,Fagainst women and girls (VAWG) at the
OL,9,FNational Police Chiefs' Council.
OL,11,FShe joined the College of Policing as
OL,12,Fits deputy chief executive in November
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FChris Nelson said despite being
OL,16,Fseconded to work for Gloucestershire
OL,17,FPolice, Ms Blyth will continue her
OL,18,Frole as the national police lead
OL,19,Ftackling VAWG.
