OL,6,FThe Office of the Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommission said the PCC has decided to
OL,8,Frun a competitive recruitment process
OL,9,Fto appoint a Temporary Chief Constable
OL,10,Fto lead the force over the longer term.
OL,12,FEligible officers from across the
OL,13,Fcountry are being encouraged to apply
OL,14,Fwhen the post is advertised next week.
